name: Donut Holes Clicker
description:
I want to buy a van to travel the world... But I'm broke and only know how to bake donut holes!

My dream van costs $10000.

I can do it!

Made in ReactJS,

Hosted on Github pages.

If the itch.io redirect doesn't work, you can play the game here:

https://clarkshaeffer.github.io/low-eff-clicker/

Any suggestions considered, I could develop this into something more
